---
title: Sticky Honey-Soy Chicken & Fried Rice with Asian Greens
description: This dish has a little bit of everything, including an array of colour. It’s a tasty rainbow! From the sweet, honey-soy soaked chicken breast to the nutritious veggies tucked into the fried rice (there’s even egg in there too), we know everyone will be pleased.

